                    Ice-cream with a helping of culture a disruption too far?
            </a>
        

    </div>

    
        <div class="entry-body">

            
                <a href="/nnbArticle/display/868" class="entry-body">
                    <img src="/images/newnutrition/culturerepublick.jpeg" class="img-responsive" style="margin: 0 auto;" />
                </a>
            

