                <a href="/nnbArticle/display/868" class="entry-body">
                    Unilever is hoping to make a success with a bold and risky new &ldquo;purpose-driven business&rdquo; that combines probiotic health benefits, the indulgence of ice-cream and support for community artists.&nbsp;At the end of 2018 Unilever launched a totally new brand, called Culture Republick, which calls on health-and-socially aware consumers to: &ldquo;Enjoy a scoop of culture while supporting culture&rdquo;
